Animation over different Beta leaf distributions

steps = 0.1:0.1:5
Œ± = [collect(steps); 5*ones(length(steps))]
Œ≤ = [ 5*ones(length(steps)); reverse(collect(steps));]
x = 0:0.01:1

anim = @animate for i ‚àà eachindex(Œ±)
    LD = CanopyOptics.LeafDistribution(Beta(Œ±[i],Œ≤[i]), 2/œÄ)
    Z‚Å∫‚Å∫, Z‚Åª‚Å∫ = CanopyOptics.compute_Z_matrices(BiLambMod, Œº, LD, 0)
    l = @layout [a  b  c]
    p0 = plot(rad2deg.(œÄ * x/2), pdf.(LD.LD,x), legend=false, ylim=(0,3), title="Leaf angle distribution", xlabel="Œò (degrees)")
    p1 = contourf(Œº, Œº, Z‚Åª‚Å∫, title="Z‚Åª‚Å∫ (Reflection)", xlabel="ŒºÍúú", ylabel="ŒºÍúõ",clims=(0.2,3))
    p2 = contourf(Œº, Œº, Z‚Å∫‚Å∫, title="Z‚Å∫‚Å∫ (Transmission)", xlabel="ŒºÍúõ", ylabel="ŒºÍúõ",clims=(0.2,3))
    plot(p0, p1, p2,  layout = l, margin=5Plots.mm)
    plot!(size=(1100,300))
end
